snippet.title: Dragon Ball Origins 2- NDS - Gameplay Grandpa Gohan
snippet.description:
Check out the Facebook Group: http://bit.ly/9emGWd

Watch Grandpa Gohan try his luck against Goku with a classic Kamehameha! Goku dodges and then gives the old man a taste of his own medicine.

More information on your new local http://www.namcobandaigames.eu/ website
